Title: The Dig
Plot: Thirteen has been in prison for the past year, but the real mystery for House is what she did to get there. At the hospital, the team treats a science teacher suffering from severe respiratory illness. Taub tries to get back into the dating scene, but winds up retreating to his old habits.
GuestStars: Amber Tamblyn, Jennifer Crystal, Terry Maratos, Justin Chon, Kimberlee Peterson, Zena Grey
